1. Sub Page(Child Page/Drop Down Page) Create:

	- go to admin panel (localhost/abc/wp-admin)
	- Pages --> All Pages --> Add New
		- Add Title: Your page Title
		- click on "Document" --> Page Attributes 
			- Parent Page: select parent page 
		- click on "Publish" button
    
2. Add Page In Menu

	- Apperence --> Menus
	- in "Page" --> select your sub page and checked it
	- click on "Add to Menu" button
	- drug sub page under parent page (move to right a little bit)
	- "Save Menu" click

